title Priority Modal Sequence (Non-Notification Pages)

Browser->Scripts_JS: loadLazy()
Scripts_JS->Priority_Modal: checkAndShowPriorityMessages()
Priority_Modal->Notifications_Client: loadBlendedMessages()
Notifications_Client->Messages_API: GET /api/messages?locale=<currentLocale>
Messages_API->Notifications_API: listNotifications()
Notifications_API->MESSAGES_KV: list + get user notifications
Notifications_API->EDS_Sheet: fetch /{locale}/system-notifications
Notifications_API-->Notifications_Client: merged messages[]
Notifications_Client-->Priority_Modal: messages[]
Priority_Modal->Priority_Modal: cleanup local state + update badge
Priority_Modal->Priority_Modal: filter important unread

alt page is /my-dam/my-notifications
  Priority_Modal-->Browser: skip popup flow
else multiple unread alerts (>1)
  Priority_Modal->Global_Modal: show generic alert summary
  Global_Modal-->User: show Dismiss + View Notifications CTA
else single alert or non-alert priority messages
  loop for each priority message
    Priority_Modal->Global_Modal: show message modal
    User->Global_Modal: acknowledge
    Priority_Modal->Notifications_Client: markAsRead(message)
    alt owner == SYSTEM
      Notifications_Client->LocalStorage: add read id
    else owner != SYSTEM
      Notifications_Client->Messages_API: POST /api/messages/:id {status: "read"}
    end
  end
end
